        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> <BR>Hello again!</P><P>Sorry to post another newbie question...I try to limit myself to no more than one dumb question in one day :)</P><P>I thought that I had seen a merchant in Ak'Anon that sold a whole bunch of the initial research words that I will need (Words of the Sentient (Azia) and the like) to buy.  Could someone please remind me where this merchant is (or if I just made it up?).  I have been looking around, but I cannot seem to find him again.....I *THOUGHT* it was in that square room with the merchants in the four corners right outside the bank, but that doesn't appear to be the case.</P><P>Any help/info would be appreciated.  Thanks again!</P><P></P><P><BR>Fastil<BR>Lvl 14 GNecro <BR>Lanys T'Vyl</font></td>

