        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         I've had great luck finding words on Bazaar/ShadowHaven vendors.  Also, traders often sell words for decent prices if you're missing one or two, but always check vendors first as they are generally much cheaper.</P><P>As a side note, I found it to be much cheaper to just spend the plat to train research at my trainer over hunting down all the words for skillup combines.  Today for example I spent around 100pp gathering words from vendors/traders to get some skillups and ended up with only 2 skillups for my effort.  Each research skillup at trainer is currently costing me around 14pp and is just a click away :)</P><P>Naenia - 40th Iksar Necro<BR>Prexus Server<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
